details: Fragrance Family: FloralsScent Type: Fruity Florals Key Notes: Grapefruit- MuskFragrance Description: Experience the caress of a fresh rose dressed in peony flowers. This vivacious eau de toilette unfurls with radiant Calabrian bergamot- revealing a tender heart of peony and Damascus rose. Its lingering finish is edged with white musk.This set contains:- 1.7 oz/ 50 mL Eau de Toilette- 1.7 oz/ 50 mL Moisturizing Body Milk - 0.68 oz/ 20 mL Nourishing Rose Hand Cream About the Fragrance: 1947: Miss Dior- the couture fragrance- was born in a burst of life—an incarnate of the revolutionary silhouette Dior’s The New Look- evoking the sensuality of its inspiring curves in scent. Since then- the house of Dior has known many a revolution and Miss Dior has accompanied them all.
how_to_use: Suggested Usage:-Fragrance is intensified by the warmth of your own body. Apply in the creases of your knees and elbows for a longer-lasting- stronger scent. -After applying- avoid rubbing or dabbing skin. This breaks down the fragrance- causing it to wear off more quickly. -If you prefer placing fragrance on your wrists- be sure to reapply after frequent hand-washing- as this tends to rinse off the scent. -Replace fragrance after 12 months. Expired perfumes more than a year old lose the integrity of the original scent. Eau de Toilette or Eau de Parfum?: The difference lies in the volume of perfume oil. While EDT contains five to nine percent- EDP contains more- usually eight to 14 percent. EDPs- therefore- last longer and smell more intense.

Apply in the creases of your knees and elbows for a longer-lasting- stronger scent. -After applying- avoid rubbing or dabbing skin. This breaks down the fragrance- causing it to wear off more quickly. -If you prefer placing fragrance on your wrists- be sure to reapply after frequent hand-washing- as this tends to rinse off the scent. -Replace fragrance after 12 months. Expired perfumes more than a year old lose the integrity of the original scent. Eau de Toilette or Eau de Parfum?: The difference lies in the volume of perfume oil. While EDT contains five to nine percent- EDP contains more- usually eight to 14 percent. EDPs- therefore- last longer and smell more intense.

name: Avocado Makeup Eraser Set
details: What it is: A set with an ultra-soft cloth—in a cute avocado print—that will erase all makeup with just water.What Else You Need to Know: The Original MakeUp Eraser is a premium- patented- 100 percent polyester cloth that is antibacterial and great for sensitive skin. One MakeUp Eraser is equal to 3-600 makeup wipes and is re-usable and machine washable up to 1-000 times. This Set Contains:- Avocado Print MakeUp Eraser- 2 in 1 scrunchie + detachable hair scarf- Reusable avocado-shaped makeup bag
how_to_use: Suggested Usage:-Wash: Machine wash hot and dry with your towel load. It’s fabric-softener- and dryer-sheet-safe.-Wet: Soak in warm water. The warmer the wetter the better. -Pro tip: Use in sections and wash approximately one to two times per week.-Erase: Use the short-fiber side to erase makeup in gentle circular motions.-Exfoliate: Flip to long-fiber side (side with the tag) to exfoliate the skin. Continue in gentle circular motions. -Machine wash before first use to activate fibers.

details:
What it is: An eight-piece must-have summer essentials set with a highlighter- sunscreen- wave spray- glow oil- lip gloss- lip tint- body cream- and mascara.

What Else You Need to Know: This multi-branded kit features a mix of categories- including a full-size waterproof mascara and lipstick; a deluxe-size body oil- sunscreen- and lip tint; and a trial-size moisturizer- highlighter- and wave spray. name: The Complete Mini Oil Collection Set
details: Fragrance Descriptions: James is a mix of gardenia and fig. Vanilla and sandalwood complete the lake fragrance- while pear and jasmine are featured in Leila Lou. Madie is complete with scents of coconut and sea breeze- and Rosie rounds out the set with notes of nude musk and soft rose. This set contains:- 5 x 0.06 oz/ 2 mL Roll-On Eau de Parfums in James- Lake- Leila Lou- Madie- RosieAbout the Fragrance: This five-piece set of roll-on perfume oils is an intimate way to wear fragrance. Perfume oils are the purest and strongest way to experience fragrance. They contain no alcohol- so a little goes a long way. Apply rollerball fragrances to pulse points.Clean at SephoraClean at Sephora is formulated without a list of over 50 ingredients- including sulfates (SLS and SLES)- parabens- phthalates- and more. For the full list- check out the Ingredients tab.
how_to_use: Suggested Usage:-Fragrance is intensified by the warmth of your own body. Apply in the creases of your knees and elbows for a longer-lasting- stronger scent. -After applying- avoid rubbing or dabbing skin. This breaks down the fragrance- causing it to wear off more quickly. -If you prefer placing fragrance on your wrists- be sure to reapply after frequent hand-washing- as this tends to rinse off the scent. -Replace fragrance after 12 months. Expired perfumes more than a year old lose the integrity of the original scent. Eau de Toilette or Eau de Parfum?: The difference lies in the volume of perfume oil. While EDT contains five to nine percent- EDP contains more- usually eight to 14 percent. EDPs- therefore- last longer and smell more intense.

name: Glow Babies Set
details: What it is:  A set of clean- fruit-powered minis packed with antioxidants- gentle actives- and soothing ingredients—your recipe for glowing skin. Skin Type: Normal- Dry- Combination- and Oily Skincare Concerns: Fine Lines and Wrinkles- Dryness- and Dullness and Uneven Texture What Else You Need to Know: Developed to reveal skin’s natural glow- these bestsellers—plus a bonus Banana Soufflé Moisture Cream packet—harness the power of fruit to deliver visible results. Take this routine on the go or tailor your routine based on your skin's daily concerns. Get hydrated- smooth- glowy skin with this all-in-one set.This Set Contains:- 0.3 oz/ 10 mL Watermelon Glow Sleeping Mask- 0.3 oz/ 10 mL Watermelon Glow Pink Juice Moisturizer- 0.17 oz/ 5 mL Avocado Melt Retinol Eye Sleeping Mask- 0.14 oz/ 4 mL Pineapple-C Bright Serum- 0.1 oz/ 3 mL Banana Soufflé Moisture Cream- 0.2 oz/ 7 mL Blueberry Bounce Gentle Cleanser
how_to_use: Suggested Usage:Watermelon Glow Sleeping Mask:To use as a sleeping mask:-Use two scoops or a generous layer on skin as the final step of the evening routine.-For drier skin types- layer an additional dime-size amount onto the skin.-Be sure to gently pat- not rub- mask into skin until absorbed and wash thoroughly in the morning.-Gentle enough to be used nightly.To use as a wash-off mask (ideal for sensitive or stressed skin):-Rinse with lukewarm water after 10 minutes.-Due to the highly natural makeup of the Watermelon Glow Sleeping Mask formula- some separation may occur.-Mix the formula vigorously with the included spoon for a full minute to allow the formula time to fully re-incorporate. Afterwards- your mask should have a gelatinous- gel-like texture.Watermelon Glow Pink Juice Moisturizer:-Can be used daily- morning and night.For oily/combo skin:-Use as a moisturizer after treatment products.-Dispense one pump onto fingertips and pat onto skin until absorbed.For dry skin:-Use as a serum after toning.-Dispense one pump onto fingertips and pat into skin until absorbed.Avocado Melt Retinol Eye Sleeping Mask:To use as a moisturizing sleeping mask:-After cleansing- apply a pea-size amount to under-eye area and gently pat with ring finger into skin for optimal absorption.-Apply nightly.-Do not layer with an eye cream.-Use after cleansing and toning.-Wash off in the morning.To use as a daytime eye treatment:-Follow instructions above.-If used during the day- layer an SPF that is safe for eye area on top of formula.Pineapple-C Bright Serum:-Apply one to two drops onto clean skin and gently pat into skin for optimal absorption.-Apply daily- morning and night- and follow with moisturizer.-During the day- follow with sunscreen.-For sensitive skin types- use three to four times a week and gradually increase usage.-For maximum potency- store in a cool- dry place- out of direct sunlight. Tightly close cap after usage. Best used when fresh.Banana Soufflé Moisture Cream:-After serum- smooth a dime-size amount onto clean skin morning and night.-Gently pat into skin until fully absorbed.Blueberry Bounce Gentle Cleanser:To use as a cleanser:-Dispense one pump into wet palms and rub hands to create a lather.-Massage gently onto skin.-Rinse thoroughly with water.-Follow with your usual skincare regimen.To use as a makeup remover:-Dispense two pumps into wet palms and gently massage into face and neck in small circular motions for a full minute to eliminate all traces of makeup.-Rinse thoroughly with water.-Follow with your usual skincare regimen.

Suppliers of CBD and other cannabinoid products sold at Sephora must meet the following standards:
1. Domestically grown hemp from the cannabis sativa plant with less than 0.3% THC which is non-psychoactive. 
2. Full-spectrum CBD* or broad-spectrum CBD*. No CBD isolate*.
3. Triple-tested product for potency and contaminants* 
4. Publicly available Certificate of Analysis (COA) of the final formula from the manufacturer.
5. Compliant with Clean at Sephora standards.  
 
Fine print:
-Full-spectrum CBD: Contains CBD plus other compounds from the hemp plant. Less than 0.3% THC in the finished product which is non-psychoactive. These compounds are thought to work together to provide a synergistic effect. This may include terpenes- other cannabinoids (such as CBG- CBN- or CBC)- flavonoids- and fatty acids. 
-Broad-spectrum CBD: Contains CBD plus other compounds from the hemp plant. THC is removed. These compounds are thought to work together to provide a synergistic effect. This may include terpenes- other cannabinoids (such as CBG- CBN- or CBC)- flavonoids- and fatty acids. 
-CBD Isolate: A refined powder that has been stripped down to contain virtually pure CBD.  No other compounds of the hemp plant are included. 
-Testing: Every batch is tested three times. Testing is done on the raw hemp- the cannabinoid extract- and the final formula when manufactured. Testing confirms the product has no less CBD (in mg) than claimed on the label. Tested for contaminants including heavy metals- solvents- mycotoxins- pesticides- and microbials.

Suppliers of CBD and other cannabinoid products sold at Sephora must meet the following standards:
1. Domestically grown hemp from the cannabis sativa plant with less than 0.3% THC which is non-psychoactive. 
2. Full-spectrum CBD* or broad-spectrum CBD*. No CBD isolate*.
3. Triple-tested product for potency and contaminants* 
4. Publicly available Certificate of Analysis (COA) of the final formula from the manufacturer.
5. Compliant with Clean at Sephora standards.  
 
Fine print:
-Full-spectrum CBD: Contains CBD plus other compounds from the hemp plant. Less than 0.3% THC in the finished product which is non-psychoactive. These compounds are thought to work together to provide a synergistic effect. This may include terpenes- other cannabinoids (such as CBG- CBN- or CBC)- flavonoids- and fatty acids. 
-Broad-spectrum CBD: Contains CBD plus other compounds from the hemp plant. THC is removed. These compounds are thought to work together to provide a synergistic effect. This may include terpenes- other cannabinoids (such as CBG- CBN- or CBC)- flavonoids- and fatty acids. 
-CBD Isolate: A refined powder that has been stripped down to contain virtually pure CBD.  No other compounds of the hemp plant are included. 
-Testing: Every batch is tested three times. Testing is done on the raw hemp- the cannabinoid extract- and the final formula when manufactured. Testing confirms the product has no less CBD (in mg) than claimed on the label. Tested for contaminants including heavy metals- solvents- mycotoxins- pesticides- and microbials.

how_to_use: Suggested Usage:-Plug the hair dryer into a power supply. The heat level and fan speed can be controlled independently using the upper and lower switches.-The lower switch controls fan speed. When the switch is in the bottom position- the fan is turned off. Move the lower switch to the center position for low fan speed or the top position for high fan speed.-The upper switch controls heat level. When the switch is in the bottom position- the heat is turned off. Move the upper switch to the center position for low heat or the top position for high heat.-The cool shot button may be used to set a hairstyle after blow-drying. Click and hold to engage the cool shot feature and release to disengage.-After use- make sure both switches are in the left (O) position before unplugging.

details:
What it is: A flat iron to create straight looks- soft waves- or curls using the conduction properties of titanium to deliver fast- even heat. Hair Type: Straight- Wavy- Curly- and CoilyHair Texture: Fine- Medium- and ThickKet Benefits: Straightens and Smooths- Fights Frizz- and Adds Shine
What Else You Need to Know:  This flat iron has extra-long- four-inch titanium plates that maximize surface area for fast performance and even heat distribution. how_to_use: Suggested Usage:To straighten and smooth hair:-Divide hair into small sections and fine subsections.-Select desired temperature. For fine hair- use a lower heat setting. For medium to coarse hair- use a higher heat setting.-Starting at the base of one section- lightly spray one pump of Perfect Defense (sold separately) eight to 10 inches from hair. -Close the flat iron at the base and glide it through the ends- repeating until desired smoothness is achieved. -Continue working in the same manner in all sections.To create soft waves and curls:-Divide hair into small sections and lightly spray Perfect Defense (sold separately) throughout.-Select desired temperature. For fine hair- use a lower heat setting. For medium to coarse hair- use a higher heat setting.-Take a small section and place the iron where you want the curl to begin.-Lightly close the iron and rotate it one quarter in the desired curl direction (away from or toward your face)- then pull through to the end. -Continue working in the same manner in all sections.

Apply in the creases of your knees and elbows for a longer-lasting- stronger scent. -After applying- avoid rubbing or dabbing skin. This breaks down the fragrance- causing it to wear off more quickly. -If you prefer placing fragrance on your wrists- be sure to reapply after frequent hand-washing- as this tends to rinse off the scent. -Replace fragrance after 12 months. Expired perfumes more than a year old lose the integrity of the original scent. Eau de Toilette or Eau de Parfum?: The difference lies in the volume of perfume oil. While EDT contains five to nine percent- EDP contains more- usually eight to 14 percent. EDPs- therefore- last longer and smell more intense.

details: What it is: An invisible sunscreen veil that becomes stronger when exposed to heat- water- and sweat. What Else You Need to Know: HeatForce technology is activated on hot days once applied to your skin. Not using the correct amount will lower the level of protection significantly.

details: What it is:  A dot duo—Peace Out Acne helps treat breakouts with salicylic acid and Peace Out Dark Spots help lighten the look of spots with infused microneedles.Skin Type: Normal- Dry- Combination- and Oily Skincare Concerns: Dark Spots- Acne and Blemishes- and Dark CirclesFormulation: Lightweight MaskHighlighted Ingredients:- Salicylic Acid: Targets the look of pores and blemish-causing bacteria. - Niacinamide: Helps even out the appearance of skin tone.- Licorice Extracts: Helps give skin a brighter look.Ingredient Callouts: Free of sulfates SLS and SLES- parabens- formaldehydes- formaldehyde-releasing agents- phthalates- mineral oil- retinyl palmitate- oxybenzone- coal tar- hydroquinone- triclosan- and triclocarban- and contains less than one percent of synthetic fragrances. This product is also cruelty-free- and gluten-free- comes in recyclable packaging- and is reef safe. What Else You Need to Know: The Acne Healing Dots are dots that target the look of blemishes and combine hydrocolloid polymer technology dressing with an infusion of potent ingredients that address the appearance of acne. The bacteria-fighting technology extracts impurities and provides a barrier from external irritants while soothing irritation. The Dark Spot Microneedling Brightening Dots use microneedling technology to help deliver results in half the time of most similar products. They are formulated with niacinamide- licorice extract- and tranexamic acid that work together to gradually lift melanin deposits to visibly lighten and brighten without causing redness. All dark spots are different—this product best addresses the look of dark spots from post-acne hyperpigmentation- sun spots- and age spots. This product is not intended for use on scars- freckles- or moles.This Set Contains:- 10 x Acne Healing Dots - 6 x Dark Spot Microneedling Brightening Dots
how_to_use: Suggested Usage:Peace Out Acne Healing Dots: -Begin with freshly cleansed- dry skin free from any oils or creams.-Place the dot tacky side down onto the blemish.-Continue your skincare routine- careful to avoid the acne healing dots.-Leave on for a minimum of six hours or overnight.-Gently remove the dot and repeat until the look of your blemish has disappeared.-Always follow with a broad-spectrum SPF and limit prolonged sun exposure.Peace Out Dark Spot Microneedling Brightening Dots: -Begin with freshly cleansed- dry skin free from any oils or creams.-Apply dot textured side down over your dark spot.-Gently press into the skin for five to 10 seconds.-Wear overnight or for at least six hours for best results.-Use two times per week for at least two consecutive weeks to give spots time to fade.

name: Soleil Blanc Mini Shimmering Body Oil
details:
Fragrance Family: Warm & Spicy
Scent Type: Warm & Sweet GourmandsKey Notes: Bergamot- Pistachio- Coco De Mer
Fragrance Description: This silky and lightweight body oil captures the sultry effect of sunkissed summer skin and tempts the senses with a fragrance of scorching sensuality. It illuminates the skin with shimmers of gold and platinum leaf. 
About the Fragrance: The captivating fragrance wraps a bouquet of white florals in a golden- amber-sandalwood embrace as tempting as a white-sand beach- as irresistible as the perfect tan.
how_to_use: Suggested Usage:-Fragrance is intensified by the warmth of your own body. Apply in the creases of your knees and elbows for a longer-lasting- stronger scent. -After applying- avoid rubbing or dabbing skin. This breaks down the fragrance- causing it to wear off more quickly. -If you prefer placing fragrance on your wrists- be sure to reapply after frequent hand-washing- as this tends to rinse off the scent. -Replace fragrance after 12 months. Expired perfumes more than a year old lose the integrity of the original scent. Eau de Toilette or Eau de Parfum?: The difference lies in the volume of perfume oil. While EDT contains five to nine percent- EDP contains more- usually eight to 14 percent. EDPs- therefore- last longer and smell more intense.

details: Fragrance Family: FreshScent Type: Fresh FloralsKey Notes: Orange Blossom- Jasmine Sambac- TuberoseFragrance Description: The perfume opens with notes of luminous orange blossom from North Africa and roses from Turkey and Morocco- but in its heart- this refreshed blend comes true: Egyptian jasmine sambac is splashed with a watery uplift- and the ever-voluptuous tuberose is made gentler by a textured sensation of freshness.
how_to_use: Suggested Usage:-Fragrance is intensified by the warmth of your own body. Apply in the creases of your knees and elbows for a longer-lasting- stronger scent. -After applying- avoid rubbing or dabbing skin. This breaks down the fragrance- causing it to wear off more quickly. -If you prefer placing fragrance on your wrists- be sure to reapply after frequent hand-washing- as this tends to rinse off the scent. -Replace fragrance after 12 months. Expired perfumes more than a year old lose the integrity of the original scent. Eau de Toilette or Eau de Parfum?: The difference lies in the volume of perfume oil. While EDT contains five to nine percent- EDP contains more- usually eight to 14 percent. EDPs- therefore- last longer and smell more intense.

details: Fragrance Family: Warm & SpicyScent Type: Woody SpicesKey Notes: Italian Bergamot- Clove Buds- Vetiver Haiti OrpurFragrance Description: Toy Boy is the new- exclusive fragrance by Moschino that reinterprets elegance with a touch of irony. It speaks to a unique- dynamic- enthusiastic- and passionate person.
how_to_use: Suggested Usage:-Fragrance is intensified by the warmth of your own body. Apply in the creases of your knees and elbows for a longer-lasting- stronger scent. -After applying- avoid rubbing or dabbing skin. This breaks down the fragrance- causing it to wear off more quickly. -If you prefer placing fragrance on your wrists- be sure to reapply after frequent hand-washing- as this tends to rinse off the scent. -Replace fragrance after 12 months. Expired perfumes more than a year old lose the integrity of the original scent. Eau de Toilette or Eau de Parfum?: The difference lies in the volume of perfume oil. While EDT contains five to nine percent- EDP contains more- usually eight to 14 percent. EDPs- therefore- last longer and smell more intense.
ingredients: Alchohol Denat. (SD Alchohol 39-C)- Parfum (Fragrance)- Aqua (Water)- Limonene- Linalool- Eugenol- Cinnamal- Citral- Isoeugenol.

name: Acne Cleansing and Blemish Minimizing Brush Head
details: What it is:  An ultra-soft brush head that helps to clear and prevent breakouts by removing blemish-causing impurities in skin prone to blemishes- blackheads- and clogged pores.Skin Type: Oily- Normal- Dry- and Combination Skincare Concerns: Blemishes- Pores- and Fine Lines and WrinklesIngredient Callouts: This product comes in recyclable packaging. What Else You Need to Know:  Correct and prevent blemishes- reduce redness- and minimize the appearance of pores with the Acne Cleansing Brush Head designed for skin prone to blemishes- blackheads- and clogged pores. It is packed with more bristles per tuft for an ultra-soft feel to gently whisk away dead skin- sebum- and other pore-clogging impurities.Because the foundation of any good blemish-fighting regimen begins with a better cleanse.This device has been dermatologist tested for safety and gentleness. It’s suited for sensitive- blemish-prone skin and all ages—even teenagers. Ideal for skin with mild to moderate blemishes and breakouts.Clinical Results: After a 4-week consumer study: - 98% agreed the brush feels gentle- soft- comfortable- and pleasant- 94% would recommend a routine using the Acne Cleansing Brush Head with Clarisonic Skincare Pore & Blemish Acne Cleanser- 90% agreed skin felt deeply clean
how_to_use: Suggested Usage:To attach:-Firmly grip the brush head ring and rotate clockwise into the handle. -Once the brush head is attached to your Clarisonic device- the replacement indicator will activate automatically.To detach:-Rotate counter-clockwise.-When you first attach your acne brush head to your Clarisonic facial cleansing device the brush head- the replacement indicator will activate automatically. The built-in time strip in the brush head will slowly turn over time and use to let you know when it’s time to change your brush head for optimal results.To use:-Moisten skin and brush head.-Apply your favorite cleanser to the brush. For maximum effectiveness to clear and prevent acne- use the Clarisonic Pore and Blemish Acne Cleanser.-Begin cleansing on forehead- then nose and chin- and finish at cheeks. Gently glide across skin in a circular motion. -Rinse brush head and skin- and pat dry.-Gentle enough for twice daily use.Note: Keep the brush head flush to the skin. Pressing too hard will impede the oscillation of the bristles and will impede effectiveness.To clean:-After use- rinse thoroughly with warm water.-Weekly- remove brush head from the handle and wash with liquid soap and water.-New brush head replacement indicator time strip turns red when it’s time to replace the brush head to guarantee optimal results. Precautions:-Do not use with a facial cleanser containing jagged exfoliating particles such as shells.-All Clarisonic cleansing devices and brush heads are waterproof. However- do not charge your Clarisonic cleansing device near water. -Read and follow all packaging instructions before use.-Clarisonic cannot guarantee the efficacy- durability- or long-term impact on the device itself of using brush heads not engineered by Clarisonic.

details:

A lightweight- daily skin defense serum that shields against daily pollution and blue light generated by computers and phones to help fight environmental aggressors that cause aging.

name: The Littles™
details: What it is: A kit that contains eight bestsellers to mix for AM and PM skincare routines—start here to take a #drunkbreak.Skin Type: Normal- Dry- Combination- and Oily Skincare Concerns: Fine Lines and Wrinkles- Dullness and Uneven Texture- and Loss of Firmness and Elasticity What Else You Need to Know: Use this kit exclusively to reset skin to a visibly healthy- balanced- glowing state. Much like you choose ingredients for your daily smoothie based on your body’s cravings- pick products for AM/PM skincare smoothies based on how your skin feels. Listen to your skin- it doesn’t always need the same thing.Drunk Elephant Difference: Drunk Elephant is clean- but in their opinion- “clean” is not enough when it comes to caring for skin. They make “Clean Compatible” skincare. Drunk Elephant is committed to using only ingredients that either directly benefit the skin’s health or support the integrity and effectiveness of their formulations. They never take into account an ingredient’s synthetic or natural status- but instead choose based on biocompatibility. You won’t find what they call the “Suspicious 6” in their products (essential oils- drying alcohols- silicones- chemical sunscreens- fragrances/dyes- and SLS) making them- in their opinion- appropriate for all skin. They believe that these six ubiquitous ingredients are at the root of almost every skin issue we see and when entirely removed from one’s routine (“a drunk break”)- skin can reset and return to a healthy- balanced state. It is equally- if not more- important what we leave out of the products as what we put in. This ingredient-elimination diet inspired the #barewithus Instagram movement- a collection of bare-faced selfies chronicling the Drunk Elephant journeys of people who have found success using the line and renewed confidence in their own skin. When formulating the products- they focus on biocompatibility- pH levels- and safety- always making sure that the active ingredients are at efficacious levels and remain respectful and always supportive of skin’s acid mantle.Drunk Elephant is a supporter of IEF (International Elephant Foundation) and is cruelty-free.Free of essential oils- silicones- fragrance- and PEGs. Irritant-free. This Set Contains:- 1 oz/ 30 mL Beste™ No.9 Jelly Cleanser- 0.27 oz/ 8 mL Virgin Marula Luxury Facial Oil- 0.27 oz/ 8 mL C-Firma™ Day Serum- 0.27 oz/ 8 mL B-Hydra™ Intensive Hydration Serum- 0.5 oz/ 15 mL Protini™ Polypeptide Cream- 0.5 oz/ 15 mL Umbra Sheer™ Physical Daily Defense SPF 30- 0.27 oz/ 8 mL T.L.C. Framboos™ Glycolic Night Serum- 0.16 oz/ 5 mL C-Tango™ Multivitamin Eye CreamClean at SephoraClean at Sephora is formulated without a list of over 50 ingredients- including sulfates (SLS and SLES)- parabens- phthalates- and more. For the full list- check out the Ingredients tab.
how_to_use: Suggested Usage:Beste™ No. 9 Jelly Cleanser: -Squeeze Beste™ No. 9 into palm and gently massage over wet or dry skin. -Add water to lather. -Rinse well and pat dry. -Use nightly or in alternation with the other Drunk Elephant cleansers. -Tip: We recommend skipping the morning cleanse as it’s not necessary if you’ve cleansed your skin the night before. C-Firma™ Day Serum:-In the morning- apply evenly to clean- dry face- neck- chest- and back of hands. -Tip: C-Firma™ contains pure l-ascorbic acid and is best when fresh- so use immediately and don’t stock up. -After first use- may be stored in the refrigerator to help maintain its potent antioxidant activity and effectiveness. B-Hydra™ Intensive Hydration Serum:-Apply B-Hydra™ to face- neck- chest- hands- or any place on your body needing increased hydration. -Mix with any serum- cream- or oil to lock it in.-Pro-vitamin B5 is well known to complement vitamin C- so try mixing it with C-Firma™.-Tip: Exfoliate regularly to ensure maximum absorptionT.L.C. Framboos™ Glycolic Night Serum:-At night- apply to a clean- dry face- neck- chest- and backs of hands- avoiding the eye area. -Mix with Drunk Elephant’s Virgin Marula Luxury Facial Oil for maximum effectiveness. -Note: Slight tingling may be experienced- particularly for the first few days of application. -This typically dissipates as your skin becomes adjusted. -Start slowly. -Use the product every other night- alternating with Drunk Elephant’s Virgin Marula Oil as necessary.Virgin Marula Luxury Facial Oil:-Apply two to three drops to face- neck- chest- hands- cuticles- or any place on your body needing increased moisture without any greasy residue for balanced-- glowing-- healthy-looking skin. -Use with Drunk Elephant cleansers- serums- and sun protection as part of your complete Drunk Elephant skincare routine.-Tip: Apply one to two drops under eyes to help minimize the look of fine lines and revive fragile skin.Protini™ Polypeptide Cream:-Apply morning and night to clean- dry skin for a vital dose of protein and replenishing moisture the skin needs to retain its youthful appearance. -Tip: Think of Protini™ in your Drunk Elephant skincare routine like adding a shot of protein to your smoothie every day. Umbra Sheer™ Physical Daily Defense SPF 30:-Every morning- apply evenly onto face- neck- chest- and backs of hands.  C-Tango™ Multivitamin Eye Cream:-Gently pat a pump of C-Tango™ around the eye area using your ring finger. -May be mixed with Shaba Complex™ Eye Serum. -Tip: Leave C-Tango™ in the fridge for a cooling- soothing treatment.

name: Supersonic™ Hair Dryer Limited Edition Gift Set
details:
What it is:  The Dyson Supersonic™ hair dryer is engineered to protect hair from extreme heat damage- with the fastest drying* and controlled styling to help increase smoothness by 75%- increase shine by up to 132% and decrease frizz and flyaways by up to 61%.** The limited edition gift set features Dyson Supersonic™ in fuchsia and nickel- with a Dyson-designed 1.4” vented round brush and detangling comb. 

Hair Type: Straight- Wavy- Curly- and Coily

Hair Texture: Fine- Medium- and Thick

Key Benefits:  Protects from Heat and Adds Shine

What Else You Need to Know: 
Fastest drying+:The small- powerful Dyson digital motor V9 combined with Air Multiplier technology- produces a high-velocity jet of controlled air- for the fastest drying+ and precision styling.

Helps prevents extreme heat damage: Intelligent heat control measures the air temperature over 40 times a second- to prevent extreme heat damage.

Engineered for different hair types: Through research in our hair laboratories Dyson has engineered a range of attachments designed to style different hair types.

Lightweight and balanced: Dyson has turned convention on its head and put the motor in the handle- completely rebalancing the dryer's weight and shape.

Magnetic attachments: The Dyson Supersonic hair dryer comes with magnetic attachments- so you can adjust quickly and easily.

Acoustically tuned: The powerful motor is tuned to produce one inaudible frequency.

Precise speed and heat settings: Delivers fast drying and styling- regular drying- and gentle drying with a constant cool flow.

Negative ions: Help reduce static in the hair.

Cool to touch: With Heat Shield technology- the surfaces of the attachments stay cool. Even during close-up styling.

This product is a 2016 and 2017 Allure Best of Beauty award winner and a 2017 Allure Reader’s Choice award winner. 

* Fastest drying as tested on real hair by an external lab against the hair dryer market.
** vs. naturally dried hair. Results may vary by hair type. 

This Set Contains:
- Dyson Supersonic™ hair dryer
- 1.4” round brush
- Detangling comb
- Smoothing nozzle
- Styling concentrator
- Diffuser
- Non-slip mat
- Storage hanger
how_to_use: Suggested Usage:Dyson smoothing nozzle:-Dries hair gently with a smooth- wide airflow- allowing you to dry and style at the same time. This can be used to rough up dry hair. -Attach the nozzle vertically- which will gently move the hair from side-to-side- helping lift the hair. Think of this as fanning your hair with the nozzle standing upright. -To finish your style- rotate the nozzle to point air flow down (switch to horizontal) the hair shaft- using your fingers or a brush to guide it. -Consider switching to a lower heat setting to avoid over-drying the hair.Dyson styling concentrator: -High-velocity- focused air that lets you style one section at a time–without worrying about disturbing the rest.-Rotate the styling concentrator to match the direction you’re styling in. -Use a round brush to guide your hair and create your style. Dyson diffuser: -Engineered to disperse air evenly around each of your curls. Simulates natural drying to help reduce frizz and improve definition.-To start- don’t comb or brush your hair once washed; you don't want to interrupt your hair’s natural curl. Tip: comb it out while you condition and you should be good to go.-Gather your hair in the diffuser- starting at the tips. -Very gently push the hair upwards. -The trick is to move your natural curls as little as possible- so try not to brush or touch your hair and stick to the lowest airflow setting.

how_to_use: Suggested Usage:-Fragrance is intensified by the warmth of your own body. Apply in the creases of your knees and elbows for a longer-lasting- stronger scent. -After applying- avoid rubbing or dabbing skin. This breaks down the fragrance- causing it to wear off more quickly. -If you prefer placing fragrance on your wrists- be sure to reapply after frequent hand-washing- as this tends to rinse off the scent. -Replace fragrance after 12 months. Expired perfumes more than a year old lose the integrity of the original scent. Eau de Toilette or Eau de Parfum?: The difference lies in the volume of perfume oil. While EDT contains five to nine percent- EDP contains more- usually eight to 14 percent. EDPs- therefore- last longer and smell more intense.

-Sun protection measures: spending time in the sun increases your risk of skin cancer and early skin aging. To decrease this risk- regularly use a sunscreen with a broad-spectrum SPF of 15 or higher and other sun protection measures including: limit time in the sun- especially from 10AM to 2PM; and wear long-sleeve shirts- pants- hats- and sunglasses.
 Precautions:-For external use only. 
-Flammable: contents under pressure. Do not puncture or incinerate. Do not store at temperatures above 120 degrees Fahrenheit. Do not use in presence of flame or spark- or while smoking. 
-Do not use on damaged or broken skin. 
-Keep away from face to avoid breathing in.
-Keep out of eyes. Rinse with water to remove. 
-Stop use and ask doctor if skin rash occurs. 
-Keep out of reach of children. 
-If product is swallowed- get medical help or contact poison control center right away.

how_to_use: Suggested Usage:-Fragrance is intensified by the warmth of your own body. Apply in the creases of your knees and elbows for a longer-lasting- stronger scent. -After applying- avoid rubbing or dabbing skin. This breaks down the fragrance- causing it to wear off more quickly. -If you prefer placing fragrance on your wrists- be sure to reapply after frequent hand-washing- as this tends to rinse off the scent. -Replace fragrance after 12 months. Expired perfumes more than a year old lose the integrity of the original scent. Eau de Toilette or Eau de Parfum?: The difference lies in the volume of perfume oil. While EDT contains five to nine percent- EDP contains more- usually eight to 14 percent. EDPs- therefore- last longer and smell more intense.

Patrick's technique: "For that full- brushed-up look I've been doing- I start by really wetting the product before picking it up with my spoolie. Then I comb the product through the brows- brushing upwards- making sure each hair is thoroughly coated and wet. Let the product dry down for a second- just enough to get tacky- then use the handle of your spoolie to press the hair into place in an upward motion- "laminating" the brows against the skin. You can then gently brush through and shape them as you want. The great thing about this formula is that it's strong- but not stiff or crunchy- and you can just brush through and reshape throughout the day."

Skin Type: Normal- Dry- Combination- and Oily Skincare Concerns: Pores- Dullness- and Uneven Texture Formulation: Lightweight LiquidHighlighted Ingredients:- Salicylic Acid: Exfoliates the skin to help reduce the look of pores- skin imperfections- and photodamage. - Lactic Acid: Exfoliates the skin to help improve the look of dull and uneven skin while leaving the skin looking soft and smooth. - Glycolic Acid: Helps exfoliate the outermost layer of the skin to reveal a brighter-looking complexion. Ingredient Callouts: Free of sulfates SLS and SLES- parabens- formaldehydes- formaldehyde-releasing agents- phthalates- mineral oil- retinyl palmitate- oxybenzone- coal tar- hydroquinone- triclosan- and triclocarban- and contains less than one percent of synthetic fragrances. This product is also cruelty-free. What Else You Need to Know: This powerful at-home peel with three potent acids—salicylic- glycolic- and lactic—helps minimize the appearance of dull and uneven skin to reveal a brighter-- more youthful-looking complexion.  Clinical Results:  In a double-blind 8-week study of 22 female participants ages 25 to 55- immediately after one use: - 90% said skin contours felt immediately retexturized or smoother - 86% found skin felt immediately smoother or retexturized - 76% found skin felt softerAfter 8 weeks: - 100% found the peel is suitable for use at home - 91% found skin feels smoother or retexturized - 86% found complexion is overall brighter looking
how_to_use: Suggested Usage:-Use one vial every two weeks.-Do not use on wet skin- make sure skin is completely dry.-Apply first layer evenly across face according to usage instructions.  -If first layer is tolerable- apply second layer 30 to 60 seconds after application.-Leave on for about 10 minutes after application of first layer.-Use a damp gauze or towel followed by rinsing with water and gently patting dry with a soft towel.-Mild tingling may be experienced.-Apply a physical sunscreen to the treated area.  -Sunscreen should be used daily after the peel.
ingredients: -Salicylic Acid: Exfoliates the skin to help reduce the look of pores- skin imperfections- and photodamage. -Lactic Acid: Exfoliates the skin to help improve the look of dull and uneven skin while leaving the skin looking soft and smooth. -Glycolic Acid: Helps exfoliate the outermost layer of the skin to reveal a brighter-looking complexion. name: BACKSTAGE Eyeshadow Palette
details:
What it is: 
An all-in-one eyeshadow and primer palette with one primer and eight blendable shades in matte and shimmer finishes.

What Else You Need to Know: These all-in-one eye palettes have everything you need to prime- shade- and highlight for runway-ready eyes. It includes an eye primer that reinforces shadow hold and enhances the look of pigment- and eight shades designed to blend beautifully and be used as either eyeshadow or liner.
 The Dior Backstage Eye Palette is available in four universal shade ranges: rosy hues with cool undertones- brown neutrals with warm undertones- fiery neutrals in amber tones- and luminous neutrals in rosewood tones to create an array of customizable eye makeup looks.
how_to_use: Suggested Usage:-Apply the primer to the entire lid.-Add color to the lid by applying a lighter shade on the brow arch.-Intensify the eyes by applying a more intense shade along the lash line and to the outer corner of the eye. -Deepen the look of the eyes by applying a darker shade under the eye- then blend.For a natural look: -Apply a neutral shade to the entire eyelid- then add a deeper shade blended around the upper lash line to create soft dimension. -Highlight by applying a lighter shade under the eyebrow arch and to the inner corner to open up the eyes.For a sophisticated look: -Apply a more intense shade to the entire lid.                            -For additional definition- add a darker shade along the upper and lower lash line. Continue by blending a deeper shade onto the outer corners of the eyes. -Highlight by applying a lighter shade under the eyebrow arch and at the inner corner of the eye.

name: Corrale™ Hair Straightener
details:
What it is:
The only straightener with flexing plates that shape to gather hair. Use corded or cord-free. 
Flexing manganese copper alloy plates shape around your hair. This extra control allows you to create the same style but with less heat - and half the damage.*

Key benefits:
- Cord-free- with the thermal performance of a corded straightener
- 50 percent less breakage*
- Less frizz and fewer flyaways**

Key features:
Suitable for all hair types: Three precise heat settings (330°F- 365°F and 410°F) to suit your hair type- length and desired style.
Manganese copper plates: Manganese copper alloy selected for its flexibility- strength- and thermal conduction.
Up to 30 minutes cord-free styling***: Delivers the same thermal performance of a corded straightener. Fully recharges in just 70 minutes. 
Engineered for balance: Weight is balanced in the hand to give maximum control while styling.  
OLED Screen: Displays battery level- temperature control and charging status during use.
Auto shut-off and Safety lock: Switches off after 10 minutes of inactivity for added peace of mind. Safety lock allows for immediate storage after use. 
Ready to travel: Universal voltage and a battery disabler that is TSA-approved and safe to fly with. 

If you want to know more…
Enhanced styling: By gathering hair for more control- flexing plates produce shiny- straight results—with less frizz and fewer flyaways**.
Intelligent heat control: Regulates the temperature of the plates 100 times a second- ensuring you never exceed your chosen temperature.
Less heat- half the damage*: Flexing plates gather your hair for more control- so you can achieve the same style with less heat and 50 percent less breakage*.
Flexing Plates: The only straightener with flexing plates that shape around your hair- gathering it neatly together on each pass. By gathering hair for more control- this allows for a lighter grip when styling. 
Ready to style when you are: With 90 percent battery charge in just 40 minutes- using the magnetic charging cable or dock. 
Maximize run time with Charging dock: Place your Dyson Corrale™ straightener in the dock when not in use and in between sections to extend run time. The OLED screen and chime will indicate that your machine is charging properly. 
Key sounds: Chimes to indicate your machine is heating up- chosen temperature reached- low battery- empty battery- charging- idle mode and service alerts. To turn off the prompt sounds- mute by holding the power and temperature buttons for five seconds. 

Specifications: 
Machine Weight: 1.23 lbs
3 heat settings: 330°F- 365°F- 410°F
Cord-free run time: Up to 30 minutes***
Charge time (90%): 40 min
Charge time (to full): 70 min
Battery: 4-cell lithium-ion battery
Flexing plates: Flexing manganese copper alloy plates shape to gather hair.
Wattage: 200 W
OLED screen: Battery- temperature and charging status displayed.
Cable Length: 10.9 ft
Universal Voltage: 10.8V-16.8V
Machine Height: 1.8in
Machine Length: 11.5 in
Machine Width: 1.6in
 
*Thermal damage measured by hair strength- when creating an equivalent hair style. Tested on flexing plates vs solid plates.
**Direct image analysis vs untreated hair.
***Exact run time may vary based on hair type and styling technique.
how_to_use:
Getting started with your Dyson Corrale™ Straightener:
-Before using- charge your straightener to 100% to maximize performance.
-Gently slide instructions off of the machine before inserting the flight-ready tag. Should the flight-ready tag detach from the machine- hold the end of the cord with your fingers or tweezers and push the barbed end back into the hole on the machine. 
-Press and hold the power button until you hear a chime.
-Use the + or - button to select your desired styling temperature. You will hear another chime when Corrale reaches your desired temperature.
-Use the dock with cable attached and place Corrale on the dock between sections and when not in use to extend run time.
-Press and hold the power button to turn Corrale off and place in the charging dock so that it is fully charged for your next styling session.
-To maximize your run-time- always start from 100 percent charge and place Corrale on the dock between sections and when not in use.
-Before flying with Corrale- place the machine in flight ready mode by disconnecting the flight ready tab.
-When on the go- place in heat-resistant travel pouch.

Tips for smoothing:
-Start with completely dry hair.
-Begin with Medium Heat (365 degrees) and adjust up or down depending on your hair type and texture.
-Select one- to two-inch sections of hair (depending on hair density) for best performance.
-Smooth hair in a single- fluid motion from roots to ends.
-Create additional details such as beveled ends by rotating 45 to 90 degrees inward or outward as you smooth ends of hair.
-To help get closer to the root- take sections at an angle.
-For finer hairline areas- reduce temperature.
-Finish with your favorite styling products.

Tips for curls and waves:
-Start with completely dry hair.
-Begin with Medium Heat (365 degrees) and adjust up or down depending on your hair type and texture.
-Select one- to one-and-a-half-inch sections of hair (depending on hair density) for best performance.
-Clamp the section of hair and rotate the iron one full turn (for curls) or half turn (for softer waves) in the -direction you want to curl.
-Immediately begin sliding the iron to the ends of the section.
-Finish with your favorite styling products.

name: Kamili™ Cream Body Cleanser
details:
What it is: A cream cleanser that gently cleanses using a stack of ultra-mild surfactants while plant oils and skin-restorative amino acids replenish and soothe. 
Skin Type: Normal- Dry- Combination- and Oily
Formulation: Cream
Highlighted Ingredients:
- Ultra-Mild Surfactant Blend: A stack of gentle cleansing agents- including coconut-based surfactants rich in fatty acids- that work together to create a rich foam that effectively lifts dirt and other substances from skin without stripping or drying.		
- Marula Oil: Super-absorbable oil- high in critical antioxidants and omegas 6 and 9- helps moisturize- nourish- and rejuvenate skin for a youthful-looking glow.		
- Sacha Inchi Seed Oil: Extracted from the seeds of the sacha inchi fruit- this oil is used for its potential to moisturize and soothe irritated skin; these benefits are attributed to the high concentration of antioxidant polyphenols- omega 6 (aka linoleic) and omega 3 (linolenic) fatty acids that sacha inchi seed oil contains.		
What Else You Need to Know:  Infused with fatty acid-rich marula- sweet almond- and sacha inchi seed oils- plus a multi-amino acid blend- Kamili™ calms while rinsing dirt and other substances away—without stripping the delicate skin barrier. Kamili™ has a pH level of 5.0 and is appropriate for all skin- even the most sensitive.
 Free of sulfates- silicones- essential oils- fragrance- dyes- and drying alcohols.
Drunk Elephant is clean- but in their opinion- "clean" is not enough when it comes to caring for skin. They make "Clean Compatible" skincare. Drunk Elephant is committed to using only ingredients that either directly benefit the skin’s health or support the integrity and effectiveness of their formulations. They never take into account an ingredient’s synthetic or natural status- but instead choose based on biocompatibility. You won’t find what they call the "Suspicious 6" in their products (essential oils- drying alcohols- silicones- chemical sunscreens- fragrances/dyes- and SLS) making them- in their opinion- appropriate for all skin. They believe that these six ubiquitous ingredients are at the root of almost every skin issue we see- and when entirely removed from one’s routine- ("a clean break")- skin can reset and return to a healthy- balanced state. It is equally- if not more- important what they leave out of the products as what they put in. This skin-elimination diet (think Whole30 for your face) inspired the #barewithus Instagram movement- a collection of bare-faced selfies chronicling the Drunk Elephant journeys of people who have found success using the line and renewed confidence in their own skin. When formulating their products- Drunk Elephant focuses on biocompatibility- pH levels- and safety- always making sure that the active ingredients are at efficacious levels and remain respectful and always supportive of skin’s acid mantle.

Drunk Elephant is a supporter of IEF (International Elephant Foundation) and is cruelty-free.

name: Sili™ Body Lotion
details:
What it is: A supercharged formula that restores dull- dry- and irritable skin to a healthier and more balanced state. 
Skin Type: Normal- Dry- Combination- and Oily
Formulation: Lotion
Highlighted Ingredients:
- Marula Butter: A super-pure concentrated butter derived from marula oil- rich in antioxidant polyphenols- lipids- and fatty acids- that deeply moisturizes skin and provides powerful barrier protection.		
- Shea Butter: A concentrated butter derived from the shea fruit; shea butter has a complex triglyceride composition that gives its characteristic rich- emollient properties and skin-barrier protection.		
- Marula Oil: Super-absorbable oil- high in critical antioxidants and omegas 6 and 9- helps moisturize- nourish- and rejuvenate skin for a youthful-looking glow.		
What Else You Need to Know: With a blend of nourishing plant oils- butters- strengthening amino acids- and a reparative 5-ceramide blend- Sili™ locks in hydration while restoring lost moisture. A blend of fruit-derived antioxidants offers powerful defense against free-radical damage. Sili™ has a skin-friendly pH level of 4.2.
Free of sulfates- silicones- essential oils- fragrance- dyes- and drying alcohols.
Drunk Elephant is clean- but in their opinion- "clean" is not enough when it comes to caring for skin. They make "Clean Compatible" skincare. Drunk Elephant is committed to using only ingredients that either directly benefit the skin’s health or support the integrity and effectiveness of their formulations. They never take into account an ingredient’s synthetic or natural status- but instead choose based on biocompatibility. You won’t find what they call the "Suspicious 6" in their products (essential oils- drying alcohols- silicones- chemical sunscreens- fragrances/dyes- and SLS) making them- in their opinion- appropriate for all skin. They believe that these six ubiquitous ingredients are at the root of almost every skin issue we see- and when entirely removed from one’s routine- ("a clean break")- skin can reset and return to a healthy- balanced state. It is equally- if not more- important what they leave out of the products as what they put in. This skin-elimination diet (think Whole30 for your face) inspired the #barewithus Instagram movement- a collection of bare-faced selfies chronicling the Drunk Elephant journeys of people who have found success using the line and renewed confidence in their own skin. When formulating their products- Drunk Elephant focuses on biocompatibility- pH levels- and safety- always making sure that the active ingredients are at efficacious levels and remain respectful and always supportive of skin’s acid mantle.

Drunk Elephant is a supporter of IEF (International Elephant Foundation) and is cruelty-free.

details:

how_to_use: Suggested Usage:-Wet beautyblender® or makeup brushes.-Rub beautyblender or makeup brushes over the soap- creating a lather. Repeat if necessary.-Gently squeeze beautyblender or brushes and rinse again to remove any excess cleanser and water.-Set beautyblender to dry on the custom grid.-Deep clean brushes by placing the custom grid over the soap- wetting the brush- and swishing it back and forth across grid to create a scrubbing lather. (Do not use the scrubbing process with beautyblender as it can damage the material.)-Rinse.

An oil-free moisturizer for balanced hydration and visibly smaller pores—now in a larger size to commemorate funding 4 million days of school with Room to Read.

 Ingredient Callouts: This product is cruelty-free and gluten-free.

What Else You Need to Know: Tatcha purchase helps support girls’ education through our Beautiful Faces- Beautiful Futures program in partnership with Room to Read. With over 1.5 billion children currently out of school worldwide due to COVID-19- there has never been a more urgent need to facilitate learning in the most vulnerable communities. This year- we honor the funding of 4 million days of school with this limited edition. Its packaging was inspired by a student’s drawing of a lotus flower- symbolizing how something beautiful can grow in difficult terrain.  
The Water Cream provides nutrient-rich- balanced hydration with the unique water-burst that breaks upon application to deliver nourishment without leaving skin sticky or greasy. name: Pitera Power Kit
details:
What it is:  A three-step introductory skincare kit that contains SK-II’s signature Facial Treatment Essence- Facial Treatment Cleanser- and RNA Power Moisturizing Cream.Skin Type: Normal- Dry- Combination- and Oily Skincare Concerns: Dark Spots- Fine Lines and Wrinkles- and DrynessHighlighted Ingredients:- Pitera™: Each Facial Treatment Essence bottle contains 90 percent Pitera™- a natural bio ingredient cultured exclusively in Japan for SK-II. Pitera™ is observed to resemble your own skin’s Natural Moisturizing Factors (NMF) so skin recognizes Pitera™ as its own- allows it all in and lets it work its magic in its pure active form. 
- RNArchitect Complex: A nourishing complex of PITERA™ with hydrolyzed soy and yeast extracts to make skin firm and radiant from within.
What Else You Need to Know: SKI-II’s story begins with a chance observation at a sake brewery in Japan- where scientists noticed the elderly brewers had wrinkled faces but extraordinarily youthful-looking hands. Intensive search began out of millions of yeast strains and studies were conducted on hundreds of fermentation conditions. Now every drop of Pitera™ is produced by cultivating the one exclusive yeast strain under the most stringent conditions that remain SK-II’s most valuable trade secret. This iconic essence’s formula has then remained essentially unchanged for almost 40 years- as the full efficacies of Pitera™ have not yet been uncovered. Until now- we are continuing to discover new things it can do. A miracle like no other- Pitera™ is pure power of nature harnessed by advanced technology.This Set Contains:- 2.5 oz/ 75 mL Facial Treatment Essence- 0.6 oz/ 17 g Facial Treatment Cleanser- 0.5 oz/ 15 mL RNA Power Moisturizing Cream

how_to_use: Suggested Usage:-Fragrance is intensified by the warmth of your own body. Apply in the creases of your knees and elbows for a longer-lasting- stronger scent. -After applying- avoid rubbing or dabbing skin. This breaks down the fragrance- causing it to wear off more quickly. -If you prefer placing fragrance on your wrists- be sure to reapply after frequent hand-washing- as this tends to rinse off the scent. -Replace fragrance after 12 months. Expired perfumes more than a year old lose the integrity of the original scent. Eau de Toilette or Eau de Parfum?: The difference lies in the volume of perfume oil. While EDT contains five to nine percent- EDP contains more- usually eight to 14 percent. EDPs- therefore- last longer and smell more intense.

name: Mini Aegea Blossom Eau de Parfum Travel Spray
details:
Fragrance Family: Fresh

Scent Type: Fresh Florals

Key Notes: Sicilian Bergamot- Neroli Petals- Musk

Fragrance Description: AERIN introduces Aegea Blossom- a luminous floral scent- that captures the sparkling vibrancy of a coastal paradise and a cool breeze on the open water. Notes of Sicilian bergamot paired with crisp mandarin and glistening verbena open the fragrance with a sophisticated- radiant glow that sparkles. Diffused with a breeze of sheer jasmine to impart a unique luminosity- scents of sun-drenched neroli petals and blooming orange flower glisten with a naturally fresh brilliance. In the final notes- glowing musk surrenders to the sultry- lingering notes of vetiver and sandalwood- as warm as the reflection of sunlight on water.
how_to_use:
Suggested Usage:
-Fragrance is intensified by the warmth of your own body. Apply in the creases of your knees and elbows for a longer-lasting- stronger scent. 
-After applying- avoid rubbing or dabbing skin. This breaks down the fragrance- causing it to wear off more quickly. 
-If you prefer placing fragrance on your wrists- be sure to reapply after frequent hand-washing- as this tends to rinse off the scent. 
-Replace fragrance after 12 months. Expired perfumes more than a year old lose the integrity of the original scent.

 Eau de Toilette or Eau de Parfum?:
The difference lies in the volume of perfume oil. While EDT contains five to nine percent- EDP contains more- usually eight to 14 percent. EDPs- therefore- last longer and smell more intense.

name: The Power Couple Lash & Lip Cult Faves Starter Set
details: What it is: A cult-favorite lash serum and clear hydrating lip plumper gloss duo for longer-- thicker-looking lashes and fuller-looking- more hydrated lips.Ingredient Callouts: Free of parabens. This product is also cruelty-free.What Else You Need to Know: Get longer-looking natural lashes and fuller-looking lips with the Power Couple Set. It features a four-week supply of the iconic GrandeLASH-MD Lash Enhancing Serum paired with Glow Recipe’s GrandeLIPS Hydrating Lip Plumper- a high-gloss- visibly volumizing lip beauty treatment with long-term hydrating benefits.This Set Contains:- 0.02 oz/ 0.7 mL GrandeLASH-MD Lash Enhancing Serum- 0.05 oz/ 1.4 mL GrandeLIPS Hydrating Lip PlumperClinical Results: In a consumer study with 30 subjects using GrandeLIPS Hydrating Lip Plumper: - 97% said lips felt hydrated- 90% saw fuller-looking lipsIn a 12-week consumer study with 30 subjects using GrandeLASH-MD Lash Enhancing Serum:- 94% saw healthier-looking lashes- 91% saw longer-looking lashes
how_to_use: Suggested Usage:GrandeLASH-MD Lash Enhancing Serum: -Apply using a single stroke on your eyelid just above your upper lash line (like a liquid eyeliner). -Remember- you’re applying to the skin closest to the lashes (the lash root)—not the actual lashes. -Use once daily and allow one to two minutes for the serum to dry. -This four-week trial is just enough to yield initial improvements. -Due to the length of the lash cycle- it is important to continue use every day for three months. -For full improvements- purchase a full-size GrandeLASH-MD to ensure that you receive the full beauty treatment. -GrandeLASH-MD requires continued use to maintain benefits.GrandeLIPS Hydrating Lip Plumper: -Click the bottom of the bottle to fill the applicator with product. -Use on clean- dry lips. how_to_use: Suggested Usage:-Fragrance is intensified by the warmth of your own body. Apply in the creases of your knees and elbows for a longer-lasting- stronger scent. -After applying- avoid rubbing or dabbing skin. This breaks down the fragrance- causing it to wear off more quickly. -If you prefer placing fragrance on your wrists- be sure to reapply after frequent hand-washing- as this tends to rinse off the scent. -Replace fragrance after 12 months. Expired perfumes more than a year old lose the integrity of the original scent. Eau de Toilette or Eau de Parfum?: The difference lies in the volume of perfume oil. While EDT contains five to nine percent- EDP contains more- usually eight to 14 percent. EDPs- therefore- last longer and smell more intense.

details:

What Else You Need to Know: Composed of two innovative skincare complexes and 94 percent naturally-derived ingredients*- this unique texture is both soft and enveloping melting into the skin when applied. The multi-wrinkle intense smoothing complex combines the smoothing effect of high and low molecular weight hyaluronic acid with nutrient-rich honey from Ouessant Island included in the black bee repair technology. The anti-fatigue complex helps visibly minimize dark circles and puffiness by targeting pigmentation- fragile small blood vessels and the accumulation of water or grease. 
Fully aware of its social and environmental responsibilities- Guerlain integrated sustainable development into its company strategy back in 2007. Guerlain's partnership with Brittany Black Bee Conservatory guarantees sustainable sourcing of bee products—some of the world's most effective natural healing substances and key ingredients in the Abeille Royale collection. 
*Calculation based on the international ISO standard 16128 Part 1&2- including water- the remaining 6% contribute to its sensorial texture and optimizing the formula’s integrity over time.
how_to_use: Suggested Usage:-Use Abeille Royale Eye Cream in the morning and/or evening- by itself- or after the Gold Eyetech Eye Sculpt Serum (sold separately).-Under the eye- pat gently from the outside to the inside corner of the eye. -Move upwards towards the eyebrow and repeat from the inside to the outside. -Repeat the circular movement- this time smoothing the skin with the fingertips. -Finish with a short circular massage on the temples.

name: Love Osmanthus Gift Set
details: Fragrance Family: FloralsScent Type: Fruity FloralsKey Notes: Osmanthus- Cedarwood- LemonFragrance Description: Discover the osmanthus flower with Atelier Cologne. Sourced in China- this nocturnal flower blooms at night- adding a fruity essence to an exotic garden under the moonlight. Love Osmanthus captures the aura of this special flower in the same way a secret garden provides a haven to forbidden lovers.This set contains:- 3.4 oz/ 100 mL Love Osmanthus Cologne Absolue- Leather case - Empty 1 oz/ 30 mL Refillable travel spray bottle- Refill funnelAbout the Fragrance: Beautifully packaged and ready to gift for any occasion- this long-lasting cologne paired with a leather case makes travel chic and effortless. This fragrance is made from 93 percent renewable- natural-origin ingredients of the highest quality. Atelier Cologne Absolue fragrances are concentrated at 15 percent pure perfume and designed to offer outstanding- lasting power and character to cologne lovers. They are suitable for both women and men.
how_to_use: Suggested Usage:-Fragrance is intensified by the warmth of your own body. Apply in the creases of your knees and elbows for a longer-lasting- stronger scent. -After applying- avoid rubbing or dabbing skin. This breaks down the fragrance- causing it to wear off more quickly. -If you prefer placing fragrance on your wrists- be sure to reapply after frequent hand-washing- as this tends to rinse off the scent. -Replace fragrance after 12 months. Expired perfumes more than a year old lose the integrity of the original scent. Eau de Toilette or Eau de Parfum?: The difference lies in the volume of perfume oil. While EDT contains five to nine percent- EDP contains more- usually eight to 14 percent. EDPs- therefore- last longer and smell more intense.
